    "通常モードでシートを作成してから\nもう一度試してください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Create a sheet in normal mode, then\ntry again."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "通貨": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Currency"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "過去の支出で使われている場合、履歴を保つためアーカイブされ、新規の割り勘候補から外れます。使われていなければ完全に削除されます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If used by past expenses, it is archived to preserve history and removed from new split candidates. If unused, it is permanently deleted."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "過去の支払者": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Previous payers"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "過去の記録": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Past records"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "適用": {
      "localizations": {
